agency.textblock: National Marine Fisheries Service (NMFS), National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), Commerce.

action.textblock: Notice of change of public meeting dates.

summary.textblock: The dates for the meeting of the Pacific Fishery Management Council's Groundfish Permit Review Board, as published February 8, 1994 (59 FR 5755), have been changed from February 22-24, 1994, to February 21-23, 1994. Start times and location remain the same.
